title: Angel Express [Tokkyu Tenshi]
description:
Welcome to the realm of magic, monsters and fast-delivery-mail. Like every Messenger, you hope to join the elite ranks of the Angel Express. However, it wonâ€™t be as simple as outrunning the competition. You'll need to be quick on your feet and mindful of traps and other messengers. Only the quickest and nimblest Messengers will make it.
Angel Express is a madcap 2.5D racing platformer where you must do whatever it takes to be the fastest messenger! Will your determination and agility be enough to get you across the finish line? Local 1-4 players support means things get more frantic when friends and family join the race!
